http://www.sohu.com/a/411994930_237556	36318
<p><strong><span>2020</span></strong><strong>年<span>8</span>月<span>7</span>日，</strong><span>realme</span>真我<span>V5</span>正式开售，作为新一代<span>5G</span>闪充手机，<span>reame</span>真我<span>V5</span>采用全新潮玩设计，<span>30W</span>智慧闪充<span>+5000mAh</span>超大电池的组合，有效解决<span>5G</span>高刷新率手机的续航痛点。</p>
