<p><span>realme </span>真我<span>V5</span>各版本售价：<span>6GB+128GB</span>首发到手价<span>1399</span>元，<span>8GB+128GB</span>首发价<span>1899</span>元。<span></span></p>
<p><strong>逆势增长，全球成长最快手机品牌</strong><span></span></p>
